{"schema_version":"1","crate":"wikiada","version":"1.5.0","id":"4b8827dd6abd1f07","name":"Wiki.Streams.Text_IO","qualified_name":"Wiki.Streams.Text_IO","kind":"ada_package","location":{"file":"src/wiki-streams-text_io.ads","line":21,"column":9},"code":"package Wiki.Streams.Text_IO","documentation":{"description":"=== Text_IO Input and Output streams ===\nThe `Wiki.Streams.Text_IO` package defines the `File_Input_Stream` and\nthe `File_Output_Stream` types which use the `Ada.Wide_Wide_Text_IO` package\nto read or write the output streams.\n\nBy default the `File_Input_Stream` is configured to read the standard input.\nThe `Open` procedure can be used to read from a file knowing its name.\n\nThe `File_Output_Stream` is configured to write on the standard output.\nThe `Open` and `Create` procedure can be used to write on a file."},"tagged_types":[{"id":"f643d25a2fab87ca","name":"File_Input_Stream","qualified_name":"Wiki.Streams.Text_IO.File_Input_Stream","kind":"ada_tagged_type","location":{"file":"src/wiki-streams-text_io.ads","line":23,"column":9},"code":"type File_Input_Stream is limited new Ada.Finalization.Limited_Controlled\n  and Wiki.Streams.Input_Stream with private;","parent_type":{"qualified_name":"Ada.Finalization.Limited_Controlled","id":"6ed6e49a72ebcf95"},"progenitor_types":[{"qualified_name":"Wiki.Streams.Input_Stream","id":"04860bea1718b20a","unit":"wiki-streams"}],"dispatching_declared":[{"qualified_name":"Wiki.Streams.Text_IO.Close","id":"813bec4f4988d697","unit":"wiki-streams-text_io"},{"qualified_name":"Wiki.Streams.Text_IO.Open","id":"8d1caba220ddb679","unit":"wiki-streams-text_io"}],"dispatching_overridden":[{"qualified_name":"Wiki.Streams.Text_IO.Finalize","id":"1cebb5ac294cfe7d","unit":"wiki-streams-text_io"},{"qualified_name":"Wiki.Streams.Text_IO.Read","id":"1c2413b3667b043f","unit":"wiki-streams-text_io"}],"dispatching_inherited":[{"qualified_name":"Ada.Finalization.Initialize","id":"02d402977a236e41"}],"prefix_callable_declared":[{"qualifie